messages.message:
@Varun Nandan with regards to the permissions, we’d also want to BLOCK the users from accessing any other app other than flow review and the solution of which. they will need to use

Allowing users in Production is not ideal and we should be pushing the team to integrate via APIs as Instabase at JPMC is a back end system, not a interface where people can run the flow

Reason being we can’t restrict anything on IB right now - there is nothing stopping a user uploading 10k files and kicking off a batch - thus we should be encouraging LRCO to do even a basic integration
